        "Description": "There are a series of race match manipulation cases.\rAn illegal gambling organization keeps offering a large amount of bribes to some race marshals.\rThey support several crime-related car racers.\rDrug trafficking, drunk driving, illegal street race games -- and more.\r\rAnd our client requests accident kills for them.\r\rGood luck.",
